-- Canon Raises Forecast for 2010 SLR Digital Camera Sales, Nikkei Reports
-- Steven McPherson
-- 2010-07-20T21:36:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/canon-raises-forecast-for-2010-digital-camera-sales-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Canon Inc. raised its forecast for
2010 sales of digital single-lens reflex cameras to 5.4 million
units from 4.9 million, the Nikkei newspaper reported. The
company raised its overall digital camera forecast to 26.4
million units, which would be a 9.5 percent increase from actual
sales in 2009, the report said.  
          
          


  


        